--- !u!114 &2632686106972015801
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 7665138859101526300}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 8facb372e829802469b98e38e5be1d27, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  textMessage: "Sapiens become humans playing the games.\r\nFirst 50 centuries analogue
    and last 50 years digital, games are our everyday. We live in the combo of tangible
    and virtual realities. We look at the screens, we click the buttons, and we have
    the sensors. On our phone new Flappy Bird and old Princess Peach. And sometimes
    you have an impression that you are character in video game. Don\u2019t worry
    \u2014 that\u2019s totally ok.\r\nNow imagine the big space and journey through
    the playground of digital memories. From Pong to Mario, via Xbox  near Tetris
    vizavi Solitaire two times left to Quake and above is Prince of Persia seen by
    Apple Vision. History of interactive  humanity in RGB and hundreds machines and
    thousand games and welcome to Video Games Museum."
  moveSpawnPoint: 14
  delayBetweenCharacters: 0.14
  positionOffset: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 24}
  rotationOffset: {x: 90, y: 90, z: 0}
  characterPrefab: {fileID: 416565165024829820, guid: 741551e08a0cc174bbe83c59c02d6264,
    type: 3}
  characterKey: 4100420043004400450046004700480049004a004b004c004d004e004f0050005100520053005400550056005700580059005a00
